Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.13,0:00:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One's a Red Whistle... and the other one...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't even seem to be a cave raider...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I ready the gondola?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the Seeker Camp, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really quite high up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Speaking of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.33,0:00:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.46,0:00:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the Seeker Camp always has a lookout on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So when someone starts approaching,\NI was told they lower the gondola for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A Red Whistle... A robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They might be feeling wary...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.67,0:00:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, are you able to stretch your arm up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe with both arms, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:00:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems I managed to re-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Something has...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,grabbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's still alive... that brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,True secrets do not lie concealed\Nin the darkness of night or in clever traps,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but rather are hidden deep within people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,By spending many moons in such an isolated place,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,their purity is refined,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and they gradually transform into strange enigmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my... Well done enduring the ascent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the strain is somewhat lightened around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect that was still hard on children\Nsuch as yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,U-uh, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! You're Lyza's kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How filthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see the boy is doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I've seen her up close... She's towering...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet she's over two meters tall...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How does she smooth it down to get it to look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,there's that white whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This woman must be the White Whistle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozen the Immovable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Daremo ga sakaraezu ni mogutteiku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sono me o tomoshibi yori kagayakasete
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mezasu saki wa fukaku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Massugu ni mayoikomu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuchiaketa naraku no wana
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinjitsu no ato o oikakeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ima kotae ga mitsukaru nara zenbu nakushitemo ii
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sono koe o hanasanai youni kodama ga mada hibiiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rashinban wa zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yami o sashita mama
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nigeba no nai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sore ga noroi demo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodou wa honmono
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nidoto akogare wa tomaranai
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This whistle... to think that I'd actually see it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... you must be Ozen... right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you're the one who found that whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm Ozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,W-well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about it from Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He said when I was born in the Abyss,\NI was placed in a Curse-Repelling Vessel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and then, together with my mother,\Nyou carried me to the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that thing was heavy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and along the way I thought about\Njust abandoning you many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This really takes me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We even had to leave behind that precious Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had left you there,\Nthat kid would've come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a pity I did what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Red Whistle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know it's not allowed...\Ncoming to a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,was summoned by my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why Reg and I\Nare going to the bottom of the netherworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh, as soon as I ask some things about my mother,\Nwe'll be gone before you know it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And you deduce that makes it\Nokay for you to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, I'm quite interested in how a Red Whistle\Neven managed to make it down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Marulk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to what these kids have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You want ME to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Should be easier for children to talk to a fellow child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have some things to attend to, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hear you out tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, both of you, here you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, blue whistles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just while you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be a pain to keep having to explain to other\Ncave raiders why a couple of Red Whistles are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As a bit of insurance, I'll be holding onto this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll exchange it for those blue whistles when you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stay the night here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And make sure to really give your bodies a good scrub...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand how bad you reek of vomit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I'll show you around a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This Seeker Camp has been built\Nwithin the hollows of a tree called a Great Porta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, construction to expand the interior frame\Nis still progressing little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the roots of this Great Porta\Nextend outside the Abyss...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,stretching all the way to the seafloor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anyone actually verified that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just speculation, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The roots take in nutrients\Nthat have accumulated on the seafloor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,so the tree can grow this big even though\Nonly limited light is reflected by the force field here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This wall right there is the inside of a tree hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it won't grow too big and end up\Ngetting all tangled up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please use this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The bath is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually used for washing Relics, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go first! I'm gonna get nice and clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Flowers of Fortitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they also called Eternal Fortunes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They really are everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, I know you're a robot,\Nbut there's something strange about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Until Riko told me, I thought you were a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I was a bit surprised\Nwhen I saw your arms extend like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really even think of myself as a robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck am I in the first place...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Marulk"... Is it okay if I call you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I also have something I find strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What might that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask away, and I'll answer if I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! So you have it tough too, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems we both have our share of troubles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on now, Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had anything that bad done to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see you two are getting on well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Reg, I need something to dry off with...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get a change of clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,These are leftovers, but go right ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Marulk, you're about my age,\Nbut I see you're already a Blue Whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually you can't become\Na Blue Whistle until you turn 15...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seems being a personal apprentice\Nof a White Whistle makes me a special case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after I had an accident and collapsed,\NMaster found me and took me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been here ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You have no plans to return to the surface?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sensitive to sunlight, so I can't live up on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:12:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since Master took me in, I've offered my services\Nas a sentry here at the Seeker Camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told that would make it so that I\N"won't have to return to the surface time after time"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's probably also something\Nshe wants deep down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly have been treated well here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems kind of scary, but she's a good master, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Marulk...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the Relics you've got in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko's started playing around with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Those won't be brought up to the surface, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the ones left over\Nafter sorting various Relics collected in this area...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're grade-4 Relics, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are grade-4 Relics, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Reg, check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This one here is my Sun Sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it's similar, the one found down here\Nhas a more complex shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that Relics tend to have more complex shapes\Nthe deeper down they're found.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,About forty percent of the Relics\Ncollected around here are egg-shaped ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though they're tools used by people\Nin the distant past...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're mysterious, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna excavate some.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to stay here longer,\NI'm sure you could do some cave raiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! I'll go ask Master if it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So won't you please stay a bit longer\Nand cave raid around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! That would be alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time kids around my age have come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to spend more time with you two\Nso we can work together and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too! I'd also like to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Marulk...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother's at the bottom of the netherworld,\Nand I still don't know how she's doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm not sure whether or not\NI should be hurrying down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm not sure, I have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's chat as much as we can today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what my master has instructed me to do, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to pee...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck... was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there, Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to do that too until a couple of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Riko, why was it MY bed that you wet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I did my best to find the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,when I woke up in the middle of the night\Nand looked for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't seem of this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I got incredibly scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So I dove into Reg's bed and that's when...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never had any reports of ghosts\Nhere at the Seeker Camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,S-such fantastical things...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a-are out there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Living creatures that look like corpses and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of stuff wasn't even in\NMother's sealed letter, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you're having\Nan interesting conversation here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um... This is, uh... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of you not noticing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it's more that neither that kid nor Hablog\Ntold you anything, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what are you talking about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you best forget what you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning, I heard from Marulk all about you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to confirm, you're trying\Nto follow Lyza's trail, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! My mother has called for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't this thing reach the surface?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyza is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your journey to chase after your mother ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozen, where exactly did you find\Nthat whistle and the sealed letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At a grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How many days ago was it, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The fourth layer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In the far reaches of the Goblet of Giants,\Nthere's this cluster of Eternal Fortunes, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and a grave had been dug there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Lyza always liked that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Mother is calling for me-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not Lyza's handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how such a thing got mixed in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but Lyza wouldn't write something like that\Neven as a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your reason for\Naiming for the bottom of the netherworld again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I want to go and check for myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fine idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to dig up her grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,B-besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the connection between Reg\Nand the mysterious figure mentioned in the letter...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You've followed me here\Nbecause you want to know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sora ni ukanderu hikaru nami o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabanete niji no hashi o kakeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.83,0:22:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayaui ashiba, suberu slope
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.96,0:22:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako to mirai no michishirube
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi no hidarite, boku no migite o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunaide tsunagete hajimeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Itsumo soba ni iru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako mo ima mo mirai mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:22:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dakara mayowazu ni aruiteikou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:23:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Irotoridori no yume kasanete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.67,0:23:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashita wa doko ni mukau
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.58,0:23:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi to issho ni iretara, sekai wa kagayakidasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Saihate no chi ni saku hana o sagasou
